@startuml UC17_sequence
title UC17 - Khach hang nhan tin ho tro
actor "Khach hang" as Customer
boundary "SupportChatPage" as SupportChatPage
control "CustomerSupportMessageController" as CustomerSupportMessageController
control "SupportMessageService" as SupportMessageService
database "UserRepository / users" as UserRepo
database "SupportMessageRepository /\nsupport_messages" as SupportRepo

Customer -> SupportChatPage : Mo trang Ho tro
SupportChatPage -> CustomerSupportMessageController : GET /api/customer/messages/summary
CustomerSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : getCustomerInboxSummary(username)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase()
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : countUnreadForCustomer(customerId)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : findTopByCustomerIdOrderByCreatedAtDescIdDesc()
SupportMessageService --> CustomerSupportMessageController : SupportInboxSummaryResponse
CustomerSupportMessageController --> SupportChatPage : Hien thi so tin chua doc

SupportChatPage -> CustomerSupportMessageController : GET /api/customer/messages?markRead=true
CustomerSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : getCustomerConversation(username,markRead)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase()
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : markAdminMessagesReadByCustomer(customerId)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : findByCustomerIdOrderByCreatedAtAscIdAsc()
SupportMessageService --> CustomerSupportMessageController : SupportConversationResponse
CustomerSupportMessageController --> SupportChatPage : Hien thi lich su hoi thoai

Customer -> SupportChatPage : Nhap noi dung tin nhan
Customer -> SupportChatPage : Bam nut Gui
SupportChatPage -> CustomerSupportMessageController : POST /api/customer/messages
CustomerSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : sendCustomerMessage(username,content)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase()
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : save(SupportMessage senderRole=CUSTOMER)
SupportRepo --> SupportMessageService : SupportMessage
SupportMessageService --> CustomerSupportMessageController : SupportMessageResponse
CustomerSupportMessageController --> SupportChatPage : 201 Created + message moi
SupportChatPage --> Customer : Hien thi tin nhan vua gui

alt Chua dang nhap / noi dung rong / qua dai
  SupportMessageService --> CustomerSupportMessageController : IllegalArgumentException
  CustomerSupportMessageController --> SupportChatPage : 400 + thong bao loi
  SupportChatPage --> Customer : Hien thi loi
else Loi CSDL
  SupportRepo --> SupportMessageService : DataAccessException
  CustomerSupportMessageController --> SupportChatPage : 500 Loi he thong
  SupportChatPage --> Customer : Hien thi Loi he thong
end
@enduml
